data.description: Beautiful home in Rockport Country Club. Granite counter tops. double oven with the nice appliances. Large pantry. Breakfast bar. 2 living areas and 2 dining areas. Fireplace surrounded by built in bookshelves. Plantation blinds. High ceilings throughout. Jet tub in master bath with double sinks. Seperate utility room. Large backyard loaded with oak trees. Covered patio.
